ory\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":3261,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/05\/21\/signs-hour-idol-worship\/","url_meta":{"origin":38872,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Signs: False prophets, idol worship are signs of the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Thawban reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until tribes from my nation join the idolaters and they worship idols. Verily, there will be thirty liars\u00a0among my nation, all of them claiming to be a prophet, but I am\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25175,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/08\/21\/prophets-lucid-dreams\/","url_meta":{"origin":38872,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dreams: Prophets dream lucidly, their hearts are awake","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 21, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ata\u2019 reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, we among the prophets, our eyes will sleep yet our hearts do not sleep.\u201d Source: al-T\u0323abaqa\u0304t al-Kubra\u0301 419 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0637\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0634\u064e\u0631\u064e \